title: The Only Nine Things We Care About On June 17th, 2019
itunes:title: The Only Nine Things We Care About On June 17th, 2019
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling bring you the news around the NFL and the only nine things they care about mid June. What do the Internet, Josh McCown and Tarantino have in common? Find out on today's episode.
